n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Winner \n| 15.\n| [[1986 Canadian Professional Championship|1986]]\n| [[Canadian Professional Championship]] <small>(5)</small>\n| {{flagicon|CAN}} {{sortname|Jim|Wych}}\n| align=\"center\"|6\u20132\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Winner \n| 16.\n| [[1986 Scottish Masters|1986]]\n| [[Scottish Masters]] <small>(2)</small>\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} {{sortname|Alex|Higgins}}\n| align=\"center\"|9\u20138\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Winner \n| 17.\n| [[1987 Canadian Professional Championship|1987]]\n| [[Canadian Professional Championship]] <small>(6)</small>\n| {{flagicon|CAN}} Jim Bear\n| align=\"center\"|8\u20134\n|-\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a\"|Runner-up\n| 5.\n| 2000\n| World Seniors Masters\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Willie Thorne]]\n| align=\"center\"|0\u20131\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Winner \n| 18.\n| 2018\n| [[2018 Seniors Masters| The Seniors Masters]]\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} Johnathan Bagley \n| align=\"center\"|2\u20131\n|}\n\n===Team finals: 5 (2 titles, 3 runners-up)===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n|width=\"80\"|'''Outcome'''\n|width=\"20\"|'''No.'''\n|width=\"50\"|'''Year'''\n|style=\"width:250px;\"|'''Championship'''\n|style=\"width:200px;\"|'''Team/partner'''\n|style=\"width:200px;\"|'''Opponent(s) in the final'''\n|style=\"text-align:center; width:50px;\"|'''Score'''\t\n|-\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Runner-up \n| 1. \n| [[1980 World Challenge Cup|1980]]\n| [[World Cup (snooker)|World Challenge Cup]]\n| {{flagcountry|CAN}}\n| {{flagcountry|WAL}}\n| align=\"center\"|5\u20138\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Winner \n| 1. \n| [[1982 World Team Classic|1982]]\n| [[World Cup (snooker)|World Team Classic]] \n| {{flagcountry|CAN}} \n| {{flagcountry|ENG}} \n| align=\"center\"|4\u20132\n|-\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Runner-up \n| 2. \n| [[1986 World Cup (snooker)|1986]]\n| [[World Cup (snooker)|World Cup]] <small>(2)</small>\n| {{flagcountry|CAN}}\n| [[Ireland]]\n| align=\"center\"|7\u20139\n